Simple Gameplay is :
Blocks can be broken same time but can not do same thing when combination becoming. (Its supports ALL combination)

More than one block can be broken at the same time.
Nothing else can be clicked after a block combination.
Nothing else can be clicked after special items such as bombs.
Blocks above exploding blocks cannot be touched even if they are combined.
Blocks below the falling blocks can be detonated if they are not moving.
Falling blocks may not be detonated even if they are joined before they have completed their fall, nor may side-by-side blocks formed from left or right as they fall be detonated.
If a bomb explodes next to falling blocks, falling blocks will also be affected.
Can't touch unbreakable objects (ice,vase etc.)

5 or 6 blocks become an anchor. Anchor destroy a row or column.
7 blocks become an bomb. Bomb destroy 3x3 space.
8+ blocks become an ship. Ship destroy all space.

2 Anchor destroy row and column same time. 2+ doing same.
7 blocks bomb name is a litte bomb. 2 Little bomb merge and become Big bomb. Big bomb destroy 9x9 space.
1 Ship destroy which block match. 2 Ship destroy all space.

Bombs and anchors can match. Become destroy 3x3 row and column same time with anchor effects.
Ships and bombs and anchors can match. Ship destroy all space.

